## Tidy Dataset from Human Activity Recognition Using Smartphones Dataset (Version 1.0) [1]

## Identifying Parameters

#### subject
Value indicating participant number from study.  30 subjects participated in the study; therefore, the subject values range 1-30.

#### activity
	WALKING
	WALKING_UPSTAIRS
	WALKING_DOWNSTAIRS
	SITTING
	STANDING
	LAYING

## Output Variables
Each value output in the HAR_tidy dataframe is the mean of variables of the same name collected per activity per subject of the HAR experiment.

	tBodyAcc-mean()-X
	tBodyAcc-mean()-Y          
	tBodyAcc-mean()-Z
	tBodyAcc-std()-X           
